attributes.action: Increase funding and support for animal rescue and rehabilitation organisations.
attributes.additional_details: Animals are sentient beings deserving of compassion and care. Many face abandonment and neglect, relying on rescue organisations for their survival. Increased support could allow these organisations to save more animals, provide necessary medical care, and help them find loving homes.
attributes.background: We want the UK Government to provide substantial financial support to animal rescue organisations, invest in rehabilitation programmes, and promote public awareness campaigns to alleviate the strain on these vital services.
